@startuml sequence_review_submission
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam maxMessageSize 200

title Product Review Submission Flow [L2-064]

actor Shopper
participant "ProductDetailPage\n(app/(storefront)/product/[id]/page.tsx)" as DetailPage
participant "ReviewForm\n(Client Component)" as ReviewForm
participant "catalogApi\n(lib/api/catalog.ts)" as Client
participant "Reviews API\n(app/api/catalog/reviews/route.ts)" as API
participant "Drizzle ORM" as ORM
database "PostgreSQL\ncatalog.reviews" as DB

== Load Product Detail with Reviews ==

Shopper -> DetailPage : GET /product/:id
activate DetailPage

DetailPage -> DetailPage : SSR fetch product data\n(GET /api/catalog/products/:id)

DetailPage -> API : GET /api/catalog/reviews\n?productId=:id
activate API
API -> ORM : db.select().from(reviews)\n  .where(eq(reviews.productId, id))
activate ORM
ORM -> DB : SELECT * FROM catalog.reviews\nWHERE product_id = $1\nORDER BY created_at DESC
activate DB
DB --> ORM : Review[]
deactivate DB
ORM --> API : Review[]
deactivate ORM
API --> DetailPage : 200 OK [reviews]
deactivate API

DetailPage --> Shopper : Product detail page with\nreview list and review form
deactivate DetailPage

== Submit Review ==

Shopper -> ReviewForm : Fill author, select rating (1-5),\nwrite review content
activate ReviewForm

ReviewForm -> ReviewForm : Client-side validation:\n- author required\n- rating in [1, 5]\n- content optional

ReviewForm -> Client : catalogApi.createReview({\n  productId, author, rating, content\n})
activate Client
Client -> API : POST /api/catalog/reviews\n{ productId: ":id",\n  author: "Jane D.",\n  rating: 5,\n  content: "Amazing quality!" }
activate API

API -> API : Server-side validation:\n- productId exists\n- rating between 1 and 5\n- author non-empty

API -> ORM : db.insert(reviews)\n  .values(body).returning()
activate ORM
ORM -> DB : INSERT INTO catalog.reviews\n(product_id, author, rating, content)\nVALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4)\nRETURNING *
activate DB
DB --> ORM : new Review row
deactivate DB
ORM --> API : Review
deactivate ORM

API --> Client : 201 Created { review }
deactivate API
Client --> ReviewForm : Review
deactivate Client

ReviewForm --> Shopper : Review added to list,\nform reset,\navg rating updated
deactivate ReviewForm

== Validation Error ==

Shopper -> ReviewForm : Submit with rating = 0
activate ReviewForm
ReviewForm -> ReviewForm : Client validation fails:\n"Rating is required"
ReviewForm --> Shopper : Error message displayed\n(no API call made)
deactivate ReviewForm

@enduml
